<p><a name="Further_reading" id="Further_reading"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Framing_(social_sciences)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Baars, B. (1988), A Cognitive Theory of Consciousness, Cambridge: Cambridge University Press.</li>
<li>Boulding, Kenneth E. (1956). The Image: Knowledge in Life and Society. Michigan University Press.</li>
<li>Carruthers, P. (2003), On Fodor's Problem, Mind and Language, vol. 18(5), pp. 502–523.</li>
